nodes.text:
A part of Miraluka Force-organization Luka Sene, Sene Seekers was a name given to a team sent to the members of the organization suspected of falling to the dark side of the Force.
Sene Seekers initially searched the target out with intentions to redeem the individual, but if the target was beyond redemption, they attempted to capture or, if necessary, eliminate the dark sider with the help of accompanied security personnel.
